name: DUNMAN HIGH SCHOOL
mrt: ALJUNIED MRT, KALLANG MRT, MOUNTBATTEN MRT

GeneralInformation.School Vision: The Premier School of Leaders of Honour
GeneralInformation.School Mission: To Nurture Our Students to Care, to Serve, and to Lead
GeneralInformation.School Philosophy, Culture and Ethos: In Dunman High School, we view the twin pillars of a rigorous curriculum and character development as fundamental to the education of our students. This educational ethos is influenced by Confucian philosophy, where the Head, Heart and Hands are important in developing all-round individuals and knowledgeable Leaders of Honour with a heart to care for and serve others within and beyond the school community.
GeneralInformation.Type of School: GOVERNMENT SCHOOL / CO-ED SCHOOL / SINGLE SESSION

SpecialProgrammes.Special Student Development Programmes O: Established in 1956, Dunman High School has distinguished itself as a Special Assistance Plan (SAP) school since 1979 and as a school accorded with Autonomous Status since 1994. We offer an Integrated Programme with  opportunities in School-based Gifted Education, Music Elective Programme, Bicultural Studies Programme, Chinese Language Elective Programme, Talent Development Programme, Thinking & Research Skills Programme, and Student Leadership Development Programme.
